---
/**
 * Problem Section
 * Purpose: Validate the pain point. Build emotional connection.
 * No CTAs in this section.
 */
---

<section class="section bg-slate-50" aria-labelledby="problem-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Section Title -->
      <h2 
        id="problem-heading" 
        class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6"
      >
        The Problem
      </h2>
      
      <!-- Problem Statement -->
      <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-slate-700">
        <p>
          For wheelchair users in Nairobi, getting around is a daily challenge.
        </p>
        <p>
          Most matatus aren't accessible. Taxis are expensive and unreliable. 
          And asking for help every time isn't dignity â€” it's dependency.
        </p>
        <p class="font-medium text-slate-900">
          We believe transport should be available to everyone.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
